  "title": "List Section",
  "html": "<h1 id=\"list-section\"><a href=\"#list-section\" class=\"anchor-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\">#</a>List Section</h1></p><p>Displays structured lists and tables. Supports sorting, filtering, and item interactions.</p><p><h2 id=\"overview\"><a href=\"#overview\" class=\"anchor-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\">#</a>Overview</h2></p><p>The <strong>List Section</strong> (<code>type: \"list\"</code>) is used for displays structured lists and tables. supports sorting, filtering, and item interactions.</p><p><h3 id=\"quick-facts\"><a href=\"#quick-facts\" class=\"anchor-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\">#</a>Quick Facts</h3></p><p><div class=\"table-wrapper\"><table><thead><tr><th>Property</th><th>Value</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>Type</td><td><code>list</code></td></tr><tr><td>Uses Fields</td><td>No</td></tr><tr><td>Uses Items</td><td>Yes</td></tr><tr><td>Default Columns</td><td>1</td></tr><tr><td>Supports Collapse</td><td>Yes</td></tr><tr><td>Aliases</td><td><code>table</code></td></tr></tbody></table></div></p><p><h2 id=\"use-cases\"><a href=\"#use-cases\" class=\"anchor-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\">#</a>Use Cases</h2></p><p><ul><li>Product lists</li><li>Employee rosters</li><li>Inventory</li><li>Task lists</li></ul>\n<h2 id=\"data-schema\"><a href=\"#data-schema\" class=\"anchor-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\">#</a>Data Schema</h2></p><p><h3 id=\"items-schema\"><a href=\"#items-schema\" class=\"anchor-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\">#</a>Items Schema</h3></p><p><div class=\"table-wrapper\"><table><thead><tr><th>Property</th><th>Type</th><th>Description</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><code>title</code></td><td>string</td><td>Item title</td></tr><tr><td><code>description</code></td><td>string</td><td>Item description</td></tr><tr><td><code>icon</code></td><td>string</td><td>Icon identifier</td></tr><tr><td><code>status</code></td><td>string</td><td>Item status</td></tr><tr><td><code>value</code></td><td>string,number</td><td>Item value</td></tr><tr><td><code>date</code></td><td>string</td><td>Item date</td></tr></tbody></table></div>\n<h2 id=\"complete-example\"><a href=\"#complete-example\" class=\"anchor-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\">#</a>Complete Example</h2></p><p><div class=\"code-block-wrapper\"><div class=\"code-header\"><span class=\"code-lang\">json</span><div class=\"code-actions\"><button class=\"live-demo-btn\" type=\"button\" data-demo-id=\"demo-0\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"14\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><polygon points=\"5 3 19 12 5 21 5 3\"></polygon></svg>Live Demo</button><button class=\"copy-btn\" type=\"button\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><rect x=\"9\" y=\"9\" width=\"13\" height=\"13\" rx=\"2\" ry=\"2\"></rect><path d=\"M5 15H4a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V4a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h9a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v1\"></path></svg>Copy</button></div></div><pre><code class=\"language-json\">{<br>  \"title\": \"Product Features\",<br>  \"type\": \"list\",<br>  \"description\": \"Key features and capabilities\",<br>  \"items\": [<br>    {<br>      \"title\": \"Real-time Analytics\",<br>      \"description\": \"Live data processing and visualization\",<br>      \"icon\": \"üìä\",<br>      \"status\": \"completed\"<br>    },<br>    {<br>      \"title\": \"AI Integration\",<br>      \"description\": \"Machine learning powered insights\",<br>      \"icon\": \"ü§ñ\",<br>      \"status\": \"in-progress\"<br>    },<br>    {<br>      \"title\": \"API Access\",<br>      \"description\": \"RESTful API for integrations\",<br>      \"icon\": \"üîó\",<br>      \"status\": \"completed\"<br>    },<br>    {<br>      \"title\": \"Multi-language\",<br>      \"description\": \"Support for 20+ languages\",<br>      \"icon\": \"üåç\",<br>      \"status\": \"pending\"<br>    }<br>  ]<br>}</code></pre></div><div id=\"demo-container-demo-0\" class=\"live-demo-container\"></div></p><p><h2 id=\"minimal-example\"><a href=\"#minimal-example\" class=\"anchor-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\">#</a>Minimal Example</h2></p><p><div class=\"code-block-wrapper\"><div class=\"code-header\"><span class=\"code-lang\">json</span><div class=\"code-actions\"><button class=\"live-demo-btn\" type=\"button\" data-demo-id=\"demo-1\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"14\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><polygon points=\"5 3 19 12 5 21 5 3\"></polygon></svg>Live Demo</button><button class=\"copy-btn\" type=\"button\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><rect x=\"9\" y=\"9\" width=\"13\" height=\"13\" rx=\"2\" ry=\"2\"></rect><path d=\"M5 15H4a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V4a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h9a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v1\"></path></svg>Copy</button></div></div><pre><code class=\"language-json\">{<br>  \"title\": \"List\",<br>  \"type\": \"list\",<br>  \"items\": [<br>    {<br>      \"title\": \"Item 1\"<br>    }<br>  ]<br>}</code></pre></div><div id=\"demo-container-demo-1\" class=\"live-demo-container\"></div></p><p><h2 id=\"best-practices\"><a href=\"#best-practices\" class=\"anchor-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\">#</a>Best Practices</h2></p><p><ol><li>Use items array for list data</li><li>Include titles and descriptions</li><li>Add status badges when relevant</li><li>Keep list items scannable</li></ol>\n<h2 id=\"component-information\"><a href=\"#component-information\" class=\"anchor-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\">#</a>Component Information</h2></p><p><ul><li><strong>Selector:</strong> <code>app-list-section</code></li><li><strong>Component Path:</strong> <code>./lib/components/sections/list-section/list-section.component</code></li><li><strong>Style Path:</strong>